```plantuml
@startuml dowjones_hammer

actor Admin
participant "Initiation Lambda" as InitiationLambda
participant "SNS" as SNS
participant "Identification Lambda" as IdentificationLambda
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "EC2 Reporting/Remediation" as EC2
participant "JIRA" as JIRA
participant "Slack" as Slack
participant "S3" as S3

Admin -> InitiationLambda: Trigger security audit
InitiationLambda -> SNS: Publish event
SNS -> IdentificationLambda: Trigger identification
IdentificationLambda -> DynamoDB: Store identified issues
IdentificationLambda -> EC2: Notify for reporting/remediation

EC2 -> JIRA: Create JIRA tickets
EC2 -> Slack: Send notifications
EC2 -> DynamoDB: Retrieve issue details
EC2 -> S3: Backup pre-remediation configurations
EC2 -> AWS: Perform remediation actions
EC2 -> S3: Upload CSV report

@enduml
```